    Use JSON instead of XACML for ACL templates (#6018)
    
    This patch switches from XACML to JSON for the format of our ACL
    templates provided via `etc/acl/`. The format is identical to what the
    REST API uses. This makes it much easier to read, write and understand
    the templates.
    
